title: Ceiling fans included, Stylish private cabanas, Spacious 9' ceilings

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Designer lighting and plumbing fixtures', '-Spa-inspired bathrooms with quartz vanities and', 'under mounted sinks, double vanity available in select residences', '-Dog park and dog wash station for our 4-legged residents', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', "-Spacious 9' ceilings", '-Stylish private cabanas', '-Professional concierge services available', '-Dacora rocker switches and USB outlets in the living room and bedrooms', '-Summer kitchen pavilion including grills, pizza oven and refrigeration', '-Electric car charging stations', '-11,000 SF of ground level retail with valet parking', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
